@startuml
title Level 1 Sequence Diagram (SD) - List Feature
autonumber

actor ":User" as User
participant ":System" as System

User -> System: Navigates to resource list
activate System

alt Resources found
    System -->> User: Displays list of resources

else No resources found
    System -->> User: Displays empty state

else Error occurs (e.g., invalid filter)
    System -->> User: Shows error: Invalid filter / Server error
end

deactivate System

@enduml